===Etymology===
{{etyl|ang}} ''[[blæd]]'' ‘leaf’, from Germanic ''*bladaz''. Cognate with Danish and Dutch ''[[blad]]'', German ''[[Blatt]]'' ‘leaf’, probably with Latin [[folium]] too<ref>[http://ordnet.dk/ods/opslag?opslag=blad&submit=S%F8g Etymology according to] [[:w:da:ODS|ODS]]: "''muligvis beslægtet med lat. folium''"</ref>.

